[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | 7 | MEDIUM | Architecture | Step 2 and Step 3, outcome window | 90-day model applied uniformly to balances of all ages. A score on a day-85 balance means something different from a score on a day-5 balance. Strategy engine doesn't account for remaining window. | Add note about interpreting scores relative to balance age. Consider multiple time-horizon models or age-adjusted thresholds. |
