[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 4. **Fix A2, A3, A4 (MEDIUM architecture):** Address outcome window interpretation, add holdout randomization, handle cold start. These prevent subtle correctness issues and implement the feedback loop the Honest Take recommends.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 5. **Fix N1 (MEDIUM networking):** Add Glue connectivity guidance. This is the most common deployment blocker for healthcare ML pipelines.
